                <Gloss>to attempt to catch in a mistake</Gloss>
              </Glosses>
              <Comments>It is also possible to interpret πειράζω and {L:ἐκπειράζω&lt;SDBG:ἐκπειράζω:000000&gt;} in {S:04001600100014} and {S:04201002500012} as ‘the process of testing or examining’ (see {D:27.46}). See also {D:88.308}.</Comments>
