          <LEXSenses>
            <LEXSense LanguageCode="en" LastEdited="2021-12-24 12:04:30" LastEditedBy="">
              <DefinitionLong/>
              <DefinitionShort>to attempt to do something, with the implication of not succeeding</DefinitionShort>
              <Glosses>
                <Gloss>to try</Gloss>
                <Gloss>to attempt</Gloss>
              </Glosses>
              <Comments>In a number of languages expressions such as πειράζω[d], πειράομαι, and πεῖραν λαμβάνω may be expressed as to start to do something, but not be able to or to think that one can do something, but discover it is impossible.</Comments>
            </LEXSense>
