          <LEXSenses>
            <LEXSense LanguageCode="en" LastEdited="2021-12-24 12:04:30" LastEditedBy="">
              <DefinitionLong/>
              <DefinitionShort>(a title for the Devil, literally: one who tempts) one who tempts or tries people with the intent of making them sin</DefinitionShort>
              <Glosses>
                <Gloss>Tempter</Gloss>
              </Glosses>
              <Comments>A common equivalent of ὁ πειράζων is ‘one who tries to make people sin’ or ‘one who tries to cause people to sin.’</Comments>
